(Lathe Lead In)
o<lead_in> sub
(CALL with data ptr[1] dir[2] comp_or_opt[3] cut_start[4] depth_reached[5] final_cut[6] cut_depth[7])
    (For now, just move to start position and set compensation)
    #<ptr> = [#1 + 1]
    #<start_z> = [#[#<ptr>]]
    #<start_x> = [#[#<ptr> + 1]]
    
    G0 X[#<start_x> * #<_diameter_mode>] Z#<start_z>
    G#3
o<lead_in> endsub
